# pyrequester

- A simple library that can be used as your HTTP Client and it is using sockets.

# Examples

```py
import pyrequester

# Get Request
url = "http://www.google.com"
pyrequester.get_req(url)
```

# Post Request

```py
import pyrequester

url = "http://www.google.com"
data = "Hello World!"
headers = "Content-Type: text/html"
pyrequester.post_req(url, data, headers)
```
# Put Request

```py
import pyrequester

url = "http://www.google.com"
data = "Hello World!"
headers = "Content-Type: text/html"
pyrequester.put_req(url, data, headers)
```
